org.opensha2.data

Class Data3D.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opensha2.data.Data3D.Builder
  • Enclosing interface:
    Data3D

    public static final class Data3D.Builder
extends Object
    A builder of immutable Data3D tables.

    See create() to initialize a new builder. Rows, columns, and levels must be specified before any data can be added.
